Reyna-Carrillo adr2872 library("fivethirtyeight") library("ggplot2") data(state_info) data(bad_drivers) 0 - Introduction: For the exploratory data analysis project, I have chosen two datasets called “state_info” and “bad_drivers”. Both of these can be found in the “fivethirtyeight” package. The “state_info” dataset is a general overview of the 50 states and the District of Columbia that make up the United States. The dataset consists of the state name, abbreviation, division, and region, designated by the U.
